Milestone 2 - User Stories
Members: Sreeja Keesara, Xianhui Li, Riken Maharjan, Daniel Medina, Yunyu Zhang
CS411 - Group 1

Github Link: https://github.com/SreejaKeesara/gift-smart

Landing Page
User chooses to log in, create an account, or login through facebook.

User Log-In Page
Uses database to authenticate sign in
Refer to Profile Page

User Log-In Through Facebook Page
Uses third party authentication
Refer to Profile Page

User Create-An-Account Page
Adds user info to database through email and redirects to User Log-In Page

Profile Page
Shows User Info
Option for Uploading Photo
Refer to Upload Photo Page

Upload Photo Page
User uploads Photo and selects generate mood button
Refer to mood page

Mood Page
Depicts mood generated by Face++ API
Refer to Playlist Page

Playlist Page
Displays playlist corresponding to mood, generated by rhythm API
Button for Spotify Playlist

Playlist Page
Redirects to spotify app on user device
